Tomas Luis de Victoria (1548 - 1611)
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tom%C3%A1s_Luis_de_Victoria

Matins Responsories for Tenebrae, written 1585
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tenebrae

This is an icy and immense performance of some of the most beautifully majestic choral music written.  Even the Lamentations of Tallis and White are less cold than this.
